ActFood and Drugs Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Food and Drug Regulations (1663 — Schedule F)
PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1663 — SCHEDULE F) in order to add PANCREATIC ENZYMES to Schedule F at a specific strength threshold to enable those products that fall under the limit to be licensed as natural health products and not require a prescription.
